history.content: Hello, I was wondering which two courses out of the above I should Phase 1. I'm currently set on enrolling in an AC course during Phase 1, so I can only choose two out of the three above due to the unit enrollment cap. From my understanding, upper division EE courses do not have reserved seating, so I feel as if 147 and 128 would be the answer, but I wouldn't want to risk 170 filling up either. Thank you!
history.subject: Phase 1: CS170, EEC128, EE147
